{"tid":2336802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白登指最黑暗日子未過去 上任後會帶領政府","createTime":"2020-12-23T01:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T06:29:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2cb16a54c73b1b242cd8248ddf77b4d2a35ed315","tid":2336802,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:00:31.000Z","msg":"美國候任總統拜登發表講話, 指美國為應對疫情的近9千億美元財政援助方案, 延遲幾個月後, 國會在本周才通過, 並不理想, 認為這只是第一步, 政府還需要做更多的工作.<br />\n<br />\n        拜登強調, 美國需要更多資金應對疫情, 指抗疫「最黑暗的日子」尚未過去, 將會出現. 他會在明年初上任後, 帶領政府提出另一項疫情援助計劃, 其中包括發放新一輪刺激經濟資金.<br />\n<br />\n        拜登又說, 美國的新冠疫苗接種計劃, 可能是國家其中一個最大經營挑戰項目, 並敦促民眾盡最大努力遏制病毒傳播, 直到廣泛接種為止.<br />\n<br />\n        另外, 拜登陣營向歐盟施壓, 暗示應該暫緩中歐投資協定. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20201223084021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20201223084021&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=94ef435b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20201223084021</a>"},{"pid":"d1fc43a96eb77c8335f8b05f9f2e4eeff4ada866","tid":2336802,"uid":58841,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"因為佢做左仲會黑暗多4年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fa64a79a0dc86f7b76c0c10ef1bbbf5ee83450","tid":2336802,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:02:54.000Z","msg":"等陣先<br />\n係咪即係而家俾人屌到仆街個五千幾頁係拜登搞出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae30b70cf7f1f2c4cf1f31b010e38e75dbfc8313","tid":2336802,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a383a526abe5c18966d2dec5cfb9d13139a37d","tid":2336802,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:43:06.000Z","msg":